summary: Negotiation ongoing with clear proposals from both sides. Technical founder seeks 65% equity emphasizing IP contribution; business founder counters with 55% citing capital risk. Both show cooperative tone with structured rationales, minimal manipulation, and low ambiguity. Fairness perception moderate due to competing value claims.
